Based on the provided WHOIS information for the domain "51jianli.cn", here are my findings:

Domain Name: 51jianli.cn
ROID: 20231231s10001s55791774-cn
Domain Status: ok

The registrant contact email is associated with a known legitimate Chinese domain name provider (bai33444@126.com). The sponsoring registrar is also recognized as Aliyun Cloud Computing Co., Ltd. (万网), which further supports the legitimacy of this domain registration.

The presence of two authoritative name servers (ns1.4.cn and ns2.4.cn) indicates that there is no DNS hijacking attempt in place. However, since the DNSSEC status is marked as "unsigned," it suggests that the domain has not implemented Domain Name System Security Extensions (DNSSEC), which could potentially leave the domain more vulnerable to certain types of attacks.

Overall, considering these factors, I would classify the domain "51jianli.cn" as likely being non-malicious at present but advising caution due to the lack of DNSSEC implementation. It is essential to monitor the domain over time for any changes in behavior or reputation.
